  _characterSheet: {fileID: 0}
  _missions:
  - Act: 1
    QuestId: meetAlmy
    Title: A Knock at the Door
    Summary: Tell Wren that her family's knowledge reaches back another generation.
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: almyTeach
    Title: The Vine-Tender's Lessons
    Summary: Teach Wren the foundations of mushroom cultivation.
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: edsGrandfather
    Title: Brightspore at the Bedside
    Summary: Explain the medicinal use and careful harvest of Brightspore.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: hollinReveals
    Title: Hollin's Inheritance
    Summary: Recognize the name and page Hollin carries.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: findWitchCottage
    Title: The Witch's Cottage
    Summary: Walk the old path with Wren and Hollin.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: caldenReconcile
    Title: The Chapel Garden Opens
    Summary: See the chapel garden returned to useful work.
  _quotes:
  - Text: No. But your hands do.
    Context: Answering Wren's claim that she does not remember her grandmother.
  - Text: Most useful lessons are.
    Context: On lessons that sound like warnings.
  - Text: Do not rush growth. Rushed mushrooms teach regret.
    Context: Beginning Wren's cultivation work.
